This paper discusses the use of GANs in creating art, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also discusses the visual aspects of the art, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential use of GANs in neuroscience experiments, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
